N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 823.7 - Records to be confidential

State Regulations
(a) All records and files of the
director in any proceedings covered by this Part shall be
confidential. (b) All such records and files of the director may be exhibited only at the
discretion of the director or upon order of the court. Notes
